---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = "19 March 2026";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Use"
  description="Terms and conditions for using ashmo.io."
>
  <section class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 pt-8 md:pt-16 pb-20 md:pb-28">
    <div class="max-w-[720px]">

      <p class="text-xs text-text-tertiary uppercase tracking-[0.1em] mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">Terms of Use</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-tertiary mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-10 text-text font-light leading-relaxed">

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>By accessing and using <strong>ashmo.io</strong> (the "Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Use. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use this Site. This Site is operated by <strong>Ashraf Hassan</strong> ("Ashmo"), based in Dubai, United Arab Emirates.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">2. Use of the Site</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">You may use this Site for lawful, personal, and non-commercial purposes only. You agree not to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Reproduce, distribute, or commercially exploit any content from this Site without prior written permission</li>
            <li>Use any automated tools (scrapers, bots) to harvest content</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorised access to any part of the Site or its infrastructure</li>
            <li>Use the Site in any way that could damage, disable, or impair it</li>
            <li>Submit false, misleading, or harmful content through the contact form</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">All content on this Site — including but not limited to articles, case studies, podcast episodes, design, text, graphics, and code — is the intellectual property of Ashraf Hassan unless otherwise stated.</p>
          <p>You may share links to content on this Site and quote brief excerpts with appropriate attribution. Any other use requires explicit written permission.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">4. Content Accuracy</h2>
          <p>The articles, opinions, and frameworks published on this Site reflect personal views and experiences. They are provided for informational and educational purposes only and do not constitute professional advice (legal, financial, marketing, or otherwise). You should seek independent professional advice before acting on anything published here.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">5. External Links</h2>
          <p>This Site may contain links to third-party websites. These links are provided for convenience only. We have no control over the content of those sites and accept no responsibility for them or for any loss or damage arising from your use of them.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">6. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>This Site is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without any warranties of any kind, either express or implied. We do not warrant that the Site will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of viruses or other harmful components.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, Ashraf Hassan shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of, or inability to use, this Site or its content.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">8. Privacy</h2>
          <p>Your use of this Site is also governed by our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-accent hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>, which is incorporated into these Terms by reference.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">9. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>These Terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the United Arab Emirates. Any disputes arising from or relating to these Terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Dubai, UAE.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">10. Changes to These Terms</h2>
          <p>We reserve the right to update these Terms at any time. The "Last updated" date above reflects the most recent revision. Continued use of the Site after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated Terms.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">11. Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions about these Terms? Email <a href="mailto:hello@ashmo.io" class="text-accent hover:underline">hello@ashmo.io</a></p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
